Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.92,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan?! Siapa dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.59,Alma,Alma,0,0,0,,A-Apa maksud semua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.88,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,K-Kan saya dah cakap,\Nini salah faham!
